{"tid":703035,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環華人行外影裙底 熱心市民合力擒狼","createTime":"2018-06-15T11:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T08:15:35.000Z","uid":29627,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2b950c0ef2565588f052fea90a817657df6a6083","tid":703035,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:47:46.000Z","msg":"中環華人行外影裙底 熱心市民合力擒狼 <br />\n<br />\n 【10:25】警方調查後改列公眾地方行為不檢，一人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n早上9時56分，中環皇后大道中29號華人行，一名女子報案，指一名男子懷疑搶劫被多人擒住。讀者阿華經過上址，他目擊兩至三名途人合力將賊人制服，按在地上，當中一名是便衣警員。「最初係兩個途人同賊人糾纏，後來有個鬼佬加入幫手。」他見到賊人手上拿着一個銀包，估計他是搶銀包，有女途人幫手報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場調查後稱並非搶劫案，而是一名身材健碩的男子偷拍影裙底，被便衣警發現喝止，雙方在街頭糾纏，一度被疑人狡脫，追出20米將他追上。警員呼叫幫手，商業大廈兩名保安員及一名途人相繼加入，合力將疑人制服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180615/large/1529029293_fa75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F1529029293_fa75.jpg&h=a2f59b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n途人合力制服疑人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180615/large/1529029296_1f6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F1529029296_1f6a.jpg&h=ca94123a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180615/58320458\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58320458&d=12zoczW74DbH1zl5oy8HVLZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=f7556665\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58320458&h=a2d1f4fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180615/58320458</a><br />\n<br />\n呢排d正義撚好猖狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a39a31759675ca807cb658290fc1941f79ee39","tid":703035,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"c